Abolished 1.10.1895 and added to the parish of Kiddington 
    with Asterleigh.

That part which until 1894 formed part of the parish of Wolvercot. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Gosford 
    & Water Eaton, Hampton Gay & Poyle and Kidlington.

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Water Eaton, Gosford, Cutteslowe, 
    Gosford and Kidlington. See also Table 2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Hampton Gay 
    & Poyle.

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Hampton Poyle, Hampton Gay, 
    Gosford, Thrup and Kidlington. See also Table 2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Hampton Gay 
    & Poyle.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Hensington Within 
    and Hensington Without.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Hensington in Woodstock 
    Municipal Borough. See also Table 2, note (f).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Hensington. 
    See also Table 2, note (f).

Abolished 1.10.1895 and added to the parish of Kiddington 
    with Asterleigh.

Created 1.10.1895 from the separate parishes of Kiddington and 
    Asterleigh. See also Table 2, note (f).
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Worton.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Wooton in Woodstock 
    Municipal Borough. See also Table 2, note (f).
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Worton.

That part which until 1894 formed part of the parish of Wolvercot. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1929 and divided between the parishes of St. Giles 
    & St. John and Cutteslowe. See also Table 2, notes (b), (c) and (d).

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Over Worton and Nether Worton. 
    See also Table 2, note (f).
